    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Athanasia》</strong>是一款沉浸式恐怖第一人称射击游戏，背景设定在一座被史前掠食者占据的南美废弃研究设施中。游戏灵感源自《网络奇兵》和《恐龙危机》等经典作品，玩家需要运用智慧与技巧与野蛮的原始掠食者相较量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演卡门·弗洛斯，一位研究员兼探险家，受召前往南美调查一座神秘设施，那里正频繁发生人员失踪事件与异常现象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座秘密与科学交织的迷宫深处，潜藏着一段可怕的真相，以及比人类历史更久远的原始恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将如何生存下去？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用智慧与装备穿越隐秘通道，揭开被遗忘的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用环境优势，躲避致命危险，伏击毫无戒备的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找关键物资储藏点，聆听曾在这片遗忘之地生活、工作，以及死去之人的语音记录。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/929fe6ee5ef6f7d729a91c604b859044.poster.avif?t=1761115244\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/929fe6ee5ef6f7d729a91c604b859044.webm?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/929fe6ee5ef6f7d729a91c604b859044.mp4?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里潜藏着各种怪物，可能是曾经主宰地球的远古霸主，也可能是不为人知的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙使用各类工具与致命武器化解危机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源，制作治疗用品、障碍以及陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们危险强大……但你聪明勇敢，向它们证明，人类才是这个时代的顶级猎手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/d7d5e71290ba59d5037845185b9be650.poster.avif?t=1761115244\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/d7d5e71290ba59d5037845185b9be650.webm?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/d7d5e71290ba59d5037845185b9be650.mp4?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/cae0b3fba01a7d50a61b30a7dd1dd8cd.poster.avif?t=1761115244\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/cae0b3fba01a7d50a61b30a7dd1dd8cd.webm?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/cae0b3fba01a7d50a61b30a7dd1dd8cd.mp4?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >入侵电脑，撬开门锁，为设备补充燃料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜行、追踪，运用智慧战胜敌方，沉浸感受心惊肉跳的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精打细算管理资源，谨慎选择战斗时机，一旦低估敌人，你可能万劫不复。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/66d465e98827d29971f0f625522126a6.poster.avif?t=1761115244\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/66d465e98827d29971f0f625522126a6.webm?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/66d465e98827d29971f0f625522126a6.mp4?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/04faaefc62eb6fa4f4fc0095414526c5.poster.avif?t=1761115244\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/04faaefc62eb6fa4f4fc0095414526c5.webm?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809950/extras/04faaefc62eb6fa4f4fc0095414526c5.mp4?t=1761115244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
